Santander Will Sell Foreclosed Real Estate, Confidencial Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-09-27T05:18:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/santander-will-sell-foreclosed-real-estate-confidencial-says.html
Banco Santander SA (SAN)  will sell 3
billion euros ($4 billion) of foreclosed real estate assets to
clean up its balance sheet,  El Confidencial  reported, citing
unidentified people with knowledge of the matter.  The bank, which hired  MaC Group  in May to value the assets,
will also sell a portfolio of bad loans for 5 billion euros, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in  Madrid  at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net  